		  <div class="__pf" id="__pf"><div class="pf-4f7bb207 sc-hwwEjo kIFSBP" data-pf-type="Body"><div class="pf-50237aec sc-kUaPvJ gjMMZr" data-pf-type="Layout"><div data-container="true" class="pf-26271005 sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-6fa2a223 pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-9875120d sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h1 mode="view" class="pf-cfc41c9d sc-epnACN iUKiYr" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-8293ddee sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">&nbsp;Can you mix CBD with alcohol?&nbsp;<br></span></h1><h2 mode="view" class="pf-2a77812c sc-hXRMBi htgpzE" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-6b207776 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Will it be OK to take CBD alongside your pint?</span></h2></div></div></div><div class="pf-27f491dd pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-44567db4 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 mode="view" class="pf-ae2ab5d5 sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-a31ea379 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Becky Spencer-Davies</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="pf-dcf605d6 pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-0857be1d sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><p class="pf-2224d01d dropcap--none sc-ebFjAB ebQNGs" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-97df4581 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">C</span><span class="pf-9f40218a sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">annabidiol (CBD) is becoming increasingly popular in the health and wellness space. New products are being made and sold in health food stores and online. CBD products include <a href="https://vapeandjuice.co.uk/collections/cbd-oils" target="_self">oils</a>, <a href="https://vapeandjuice.co.uk/collections/cbd-eliquid" target="_self">e-liquids</a>, bath bombs and bath soaks, protein shakes, creams, edibles and more.<br><br>Amongst the new CBD products is CBD infused beer, gin and other boozy drinks. This has lead people to wonder, can you mix CBD with alcohol? Will there be any adverse side effects of this cocktail? Then we look at how CBD might actually help the symptoms of the morning after the night before.<br></span></p></div></div></div><div class="pf-aa2313c1 pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-2c9cc009 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 mode="view" class="pf-63d337a7 sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-b400e8a8 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">What is CBD?<br></span></h3><p class="pf-0d2d3535 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-0064604d sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">First up, let’s look at exactly what CBD is. CBD is a cannabinoid found in the cannabis plant. It has been used for thousands of years as alternative medicine. However, more recently it has become mainstream as people start to see the benefits themselves. You might feel benefits if you are suffering from a number of conditions, including anxiety, depression, nausea, migraines, MS, back pain, nausea, sleep disorders, epilepsy, cancer symptoms and more.&nbsp;<br><br>Now is the time to tell you that CBD is legal. This is because it doesn't contain quantities of THC, which is the psychoactive part of the plant.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-e48ef9ca sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-cafca4fd sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Can you mix CBD with alcohol?<br></span></h3><p class="pf-14daeb59 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-1f6eaa67 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Nothing quite like a cold beer or large glass of red after a hard day’s work to really relax you. CBD also is known to help relax you and reducing anxiety and promoting restful sleep.<br><br>In <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6326553" target="_self">one study</a> there were 72 subjects taking 25-75 mg of CBD a day for 30 days. As a result, they found that this reduced their anxiety and helped them to sleep better.<br><br>As both CBD and alcohol have similar effects, you might notice that they are amplified. Leaving you feeling super chilled and ready for bed! This intense mix has also been said to be mood and behaviour altering.&nbsp;<br><br>There’s not a massive amount of research into whether you can mix CBD with alcohol. Although, there is some interesting information on how it can help with the hangover and help prevent the nasty effects of one too many drinks.&nbsp;<br><br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-e3578c2d sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-3fcdb54e sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">How could CBD help with my hangover?<br></span></h3><p class="pf-58cd27f0 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-f2c87827 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text"><span style="font-weight: bold;">CBD may help reduce anxiety</span>&nbsp;<br>THE BEER FEAR! We all get it. That feeling of “oh no, why did I say/do that?” The sinking feeling in your stomach as you look over your phone pictures from the night before. Or worse, when you are tagged in pictures from the night before! This is where CBD may come in handy. CBD has been found to reduce anxiety and promote feelings of calmness.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Stop you feeling queasy</span>&nbsp;<br>When you wake up in the morning and feel like you’re going to see last night's kebab again CBD could help. CBD has been found to help reduce nausea naturally.&nbsp; &nbsp;<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Ease that pounding head</span><br>If drowning yourself in pints of water isn’t shifting the headache then try CBD. CBD helps to reduce pain and inflammation by working with the human endocannabinoid system and cell receptors.<br><br>So while there isn’t a huge amount of research into taking CBD with alcohol, there is some promise to it helping with your hangover!</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="pf-fd324c7f sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-b0d605b5 pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-d029a719 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="pf-5550d8b6 products pf-r pf-r-ew pf-r-ew--4 sc-jGxEUC FRgRK" data-animation="pulse" data-pf-type="Shopify.Products">{% assign collection = collections['cbd-eliquid'] %}{% paginate collection.products by 4 %}{% for product in collection.products %}   {% assign prod_id = forloop.index | plus:paginate.current_offset %}<div class="pf-c"><div class="pf__shopify-product shopify__product-vertical"><a class="product__thumbnail" href="{{ product.url }}">{% if product.featured_image != blank %}<img src="{{ product.featured_image | img_url: '270x200' , crop: 'center' , scale: 2 }}" alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}">{% else %}<img src="https://apps.pagefly.io/static/media/Product.8ea9e282.svg" class="pf-placeholder-svg" width="270">{% endif %}</a><div class="product__info"><h3 class="product__info-title"><a href="{{ product.url }}" style="display: block;">{{product.title}}</a></h3><div class="product__info-price" style="color: black; font-size: 13px;">{%- assign compare_at_price = product.compare_at_price -%}
